What's all this panicking for?

00:14:53.630 --> 00:14:55.030
All uninvolved personnel may leave.

00:14:55.030 --> 00:14:56.160
But you're staying.

00:14:57.000 --> 00:14:58.530
Have your boss come get you.

00:14:59.840 --> 00:15:00.790
I am the boss.

00:15:01.080 --> 00:15:01.940
Stop faking it!

00:15:01.960 --> 00:15:03.290
Just keep acting tough!

00:15:03.840 --> 00:15:04.440
Get down.

00:15:05.390 --> 00:15:06.030
Down!

00:15:14.240 --> 00:15:15.270
Nobody move!

00:15:15.480 --> 00:15:22.350
[Casablanca Karaoke Bar]

00:15:23.510 --> 00:15:24.240
I heard that

00:15:24.240 --> 00:15:25.370
this place is fun.

00:15:25.840 --> 00:15:27.960
So I brought them
to support your business.

00:15:27.960 --> 00:15:28.760
Little Erhei.

00:15:29.360 --> 00:15:31.090
Don't you own multiple venues?

00:15:31.550 --> 00:15:33.510
I'll come every day from now on.

00:15:34.360 --> 00:15:35.000
Come then,

00:15:35.240 --> 00:15:35.870
welcome.

00:15:37.750 --> 00:15:39.480
You really know how to have fun.

00:15:39.720 --> 00:15:41.270
Almost got someone killed.

00:15:44.560 --> 00:15:45.360
Who are you?

00:15:47.000 --> 00:15:48.320
From Division Two, City Bureau.

00:15:48.320 --> 00:15:48.960
Ran Xi.

00:15:51.670 --> 00:15:52.600
Division Two?

00:15:54.000 --> 00:15:55.510
Is there anyone
named Ran in the Division Two?

00:15:55.510 --> 00:15:57.510
You know them quite well, don't you?

00:15:57.960 --> 00:15:59.490
You look familiar to me too.

00:16:01.270 --> 00:16:02.670
Did you go in either in 1979

00:16:02.670 --> 00:16:03.870
or 1983?

00:16:12.270 --> 00:16:13.390
What's the issue today, Mr.Ran?

00:16:13.390 --> 00:16:13.920
Brother,

00:16:14.510 --> 00:16:15.120
just go back.

00:16:15.120 --> 00:16:16.600
This has nothing to do with you.

00:16:16.600 --> 00:16:18.000
How can it not be related?

00:16:18.150 --> 00:16:19.910
Willful destruction of
public and private property.

00:16:19.910 --> 00:16:21.770
And he's the principal offender.

00:16:22.120 --> 00:16:23.030
I need to arrest him.

00:16:23.030 --> 00:16:23.550
Come on,

00:16:24.360 --> 00:16:25.600
I've got money.

00:16:26.750 --> 00:16:28.240
It's not easy running a business.

00:16:28.240 --> 00:16:30.040
Can't I just pay for the damages?

00:16:31.320 --> 00:16:32.030
No need.

00:16:33.030 --> 00:16:34.390
I'll come support your business later.

00:16:34.390 --> 00:16:35.150
Welcome!

00:16:38.030 --> 00:16:39.510
All the customers have left.

00:16:39.510 --> 00:16:40.440
Easily handled.

00:16:41.030 --> 00:16:41.480
Hurry.

00:16:42.120 --> 00:16:44.250
Quickly invite those customers back.

00:16:44.480 --> 00:16:45.960
Tell them Mr. Hei here

00:16:45.960 --> 00:16:47.440
is trying to make a living.

00:16:48.030 --> 00:16:49.720
I, Monk, invite them back.

00:16:52.240 --> 00:16:52.910
After all this fighting,

00:16:52.910 --> 00:16:54.120
isn't it just to talk?

00:16:55.960 --> 00:16:57.020
Stop wasting time.

00:16:57.480 --> 00:16:58.610
Come inside with me.

00:17:05.920 --> 00:17:06.780
Name your price

00:17:06.880 --> 00:17:08.349
so I can tell the other side.

00:17:08.349 --> 00:17:09.480
I don't want a penny.

00:17:09.790 --> 00:17:11.119
This isn't about money.

00:17:13.349 --> 00:17:14.480
Why did he trash your place?

00:17:14.480 --> 00:17:15.480
Don't you know?

00:17:15.920 --> 00:17:18.480
We agreed to
split the factory's coal supply,

00:17:19.160 --> 00:17:20.560
but now he's taken it all.

00:17:20.960 --> 00:17:22.030
Who would accept that?

00:17:22.030 --> 00:17:23.349
Your dispute
over splitting illegal profits

00:17:23.349 --> 00:17:24.349
is not my concern.

00:17:25.750 --> 00:17:27.000
It's my bad luck

00:17:27.349 --> 00:17:28.750
running into this today.

00:17:31.550 --> 00:17:32.750
That's settled then.

00:17:35.270 --> 00:17:36.870
I'll make a decision for you.

00:17:51.350 --> 00:17:52.030
Ran.

00:17:55.510 --> 00:17:56.440
Come in, please.

00:18:08.110 --> 00:18:09.040
What's going on?

00:18:11.200 --> 00:18:12.510
Will you pay for the damages?

00:18:12.510 --> 00:18:13.400
Yes.

00:18:13.960 --> 00:18:16.820
It's not easy for Hei
to run this business. I'll pay.

00:18:17.550 --> 00:18:18.880
Did you bring the money?

00:18:29.270 --> 00:18:30.720
This isn't enough.

00:18:31.590 --> 00:18:32.830
I often smash up karaoke bars.

00:18:32.830 --> 00:18:33.960
I know how much it costs.

00:18:33.960 --> 00:18:34.640
That's enough.

00:18:34.640 --> 00:18:36.240
There's still a night's revenue.

00:18:36.240 --> 00:18:37.970
You disrupted their business.

00:18:38.550 --> 00:18:40.150
It's perfectly reasonable.

00:18:48.240 --> 00:18:48.750
Move!

00:18:50.110 --> 00:18:50.680
First,

00:18:51.070 --> 00:18:52.670
from now on, whatever you do,

00:18:52.880 --> 00:18:54.310
you must obey the law.

00:18:57.400 --> 00:18:58.160
Second,

00:19:00.590 --> 00:19:01.880
regarding today's incident,

00:19:01.880 --> 00:19:03.920
both parties share responsibility.

00:19:03.920 --> 00:19:05.320
So we'll leave it at that.

00:19:06.790 --> 00:19:07.680
Third...

00:19:10.350 --> 00:19:11.280
You've arrived.

00:19:17.200 --> 00:19:19.200
Thank you for doing this for my sake.

00:19:41.160 --> 00:19:43.560
Guys, late-night snack at the usual place.

00:19:43.590 --> 00:19:44.720
Great!

00:19:44.880 --> 00:19:45.880
It's on you, okay?

00:19:46.880 --> 00:19:47.510
I'm fine.

00:19:47.680 --> 00:19:49.510
I got top marks in combat training.

00:19:49.510 --> 00:19:50.480
Yeah, right!

00:19:51.110 --> 00:19:52.270
If they beat you up,

00:19:52.480 --> 00:19:55.410
everyone at the station
would have to work overtime.

00:19:55.880 --> 00:19:57.110
Ran, you're leaving.

00:19:57.960 --> 00:19:59.690
I'm hungry. I'll go grab a bite.

00:20:17.800 --> 00:20:19.730
Isn't this a surveillance camera?

00:20:22.720 --> 00:20:23.180
Mentor.

00:20:24.160 --> 00:20:25.440
That's a projector.

00:20:25.510 --> 00:20:26.550
No need to help me.

00:20:27.440 --> 00:20:28.900
Let's go check over there.

00:20:31.460 --> 00:20:37.180
[2012]

00:20:39.720 --> 00:20:41.780
That camera should have recorded it.

00:20:50.830 --> 00:20:52.270
We're from the police station.

00:20:52.270 --> 00:20:54.200
We need to
check your surveillance footage.

00:20:54.200 --> 00:20:55.070
I'm sorry.

00:20:55.510 --> 00:20:56.370
Our surveillance system

00:20:56.370 --> 00:20:57.830
is temporarily unavailable.

00:20:57.830 --> 00:20:58.400
Why?

00:20:59.350 --> 00:21:00.790
The cameras weren't turned on.

00:21:00.790 --> 00:21:02.310
According to
the People's Republic of China

00:21:02.310 --> 00:21:03.830
Security Service Management Regulations,

00:21:03.830 --> 00:21:04.880
the commercial property management

00:21:04.880 --> 00:21:05.550
is required to retain surveillance footage

00:21:05.550 --> 00:21:06.880
for a minimum of 30 days.

00:21:08.200 --> 00:21:09.660
What if we don't have them?

00:21:09.750 --> 00:21:10.440
Penalties

00:21:10.480 --> 00:21:11.510
and license revocation.

00:21:11.510 --> 00:21:12.770
Get someone in charge.

00:21:21.160 --> 00:21:23.090
Mr. Hei, someone's here to see you.

00:21:23.510 --> 00:21:24.480
Who is it?

00:21:27.270 --> 00:21:28.530
Well, it's really him.

00:21:32.640 --> 00:21:34.270
Oh, it's you two.

00:21:36.880 --> 00:21:37.720
Little Erhei.

00:21:38.310 --> 00:21:39.310
You're

00:21:40.070 --> 00:21:42.000
playing quite the elaborate game.

00:21:44.800 --> 00:21:44.960
[May 03, 2012]

00:21:44.960 --> 00:21:46.360
Let me be honest with you.

00:21:46.400 --> 00:21:47.160
This girl

00:21:47.310 --> 00:21:48.510
is just a hostess here

00:21:48.640 --> 00:21:50.030
who accompanies clients for drinks.

00:21:50.030 --> 00:21:51.640
She insisted some creep was following her

00:21:51.640 --> 00:21:53.070
and demanded to call the police.

00:21:53.070 --> 00:21:54.070
After I found out,

00:21:54.070 --> 00:21:54.750
I asked her

00:21:54.790 --> 00:21:55.790
what would she say

00:21:56.310 --> 00:21:57.270
if the police

00:21:57.270 --> 00:21:58.400
asked about her job,

00:21:58.640 --> 00:21:59.960
and who was she drinking with.

00:21:59.960 --> 00:22:00.720
If she tells them everything,

00:22:00.720 --> 00:22:02.030
who would dare hire her again?

00:22:02.030 --> 00:22:03.030
When she heard that,

00:22:03.030 --> 00:22:03.760
she froze up.

00:22:04.400 --> 00:22:05.070
She definitely wouldn't dare

00:22:05.070 --> 00:22:06.600
answer your calls anymore.

00:22:06.750 --> 00:22:07.400
So are you

00:22:08.070 --> 00:22:09.510
going to let us see the footage or not?

00:22:09.510 --> 00:22:10.590
You can see the footage,

00:22:10.590 --> 00:22:11.270
but

00:22:11.720 --> 00:22:13.520
you can only locate the suspect.

00:22:13.750 --> 00:22:15.550
You can't identify our clients.

00:22:15.550 --> 00:22:16.110
Hurry up.

00:22:17.100 --> 00:22:17.920
[May 03, 2012]

00:22:17.920 --> 00:22:18.650
There she is.

00:22:18.920 --> 00:22:19.960
She was coming out.

00:22:19.960 --> 00:22:21.310
She was going that way.

00:22:27.130 --> 00:22:30.580
[May 03, 2012]

00:22:32.880 --> 00:22:34.310
Well, we'd better not watch this.

00:22:34.310 --> 00:22:35.030
This is just

00:22:35.030 --> 00:22:36.160
my normal work routine.

00:22:36.160 --> 00:22:37.360
We can fast-forward.

00:22:38.060 --> 00:22:43.100
[May 03, 2012]

00:22:43.400 --> 00:22:43.920
Stop.

00:22:47.640 --> 00:22:48.310
Who's that?

00:22:48.640 --> 00:22:49.310
Which one?

00:22:49.590 --> 00:22:50.310
Zoom in.

00:23:00.610 --> 00:23:02.700
[1994]

00:23:05.510 --> 00:23:06.070
Monk.

00:23:06.750 --> 00:23:08.280
I've got it all figured out.

00:23:08.400 --> 00:23:10.130
He's not from the Division Two.

00:23:10.240 --> 00:23:12.370
He's from Nanhuaishu Police Station.

00:23:15.960 --> 00:23:17.090
Just a precinct cop.

00:23:17.310 --> 00:23:18.310
What should we do?

00:23:18.440 --> 00:23:19.970
Shall we teach him a lesson?

00:23:20.720 --> 00:23:22.720
Don't you know a guy
who sells Forever bicycles?

00:23:22.720 --> 00:23:24.520
And Phoenix bikes are also okay.

00:23:25.510 --> 00:23:26.770
Order a dozen new bikes

00:23:27.270 --> 00:23:28.920
and send them to their police station.

00:23:28.920 --> 00:23:30.650
Tell them the bikes are from me.

00:23:31.750 --> 00:23:32.240
Boss.

00:23:32.510 --> 00:23:33.550
Is it worth it?

00:23:33.830 --> 00:23:35.310
Yeah, Monk.

00:23:35.480 --> 00:23:37.270
Isn't this the wrong way around?

00:23:37.270 --> 00:23:38.670
You're giving him bikes?

00:23:39.240 --> 00:23:41.100
He should be giving you the bikes.

00:23:41.400 --> 00:23:41.790
That's right.

00:23:41.790 --> 00:23:42.270
Right?

00:23:42.830 --> 00:23:43.400
Yes, boss.

00:23:43.400 --> 00:23:44.550
Shut up!

00:23:45.720 --> 00:23:46.790
Trashing Little Erheii's place

00:23:46.790 --> 00:23:47.550
was a 10,000 yuan job.

00:23:47.550 --> 00:23:49.010
You made it cost me 50,000.

00:23:49.110 --> 00:23:50.720
Making those migrant worker punks

00:23:50.720 --> 00:23:51.880
pool money to bail me out.

00:23:51.880 --> 00:23:53.310
Have I no shame?

00:23:54.440 --> 00:23:55.440
Boss,

00:23:55.480 --> 00:23:56.790
I didn't do it on purpose.

00:23:56.790 --> 00:23:58.030
-Boss.
-I asked you to ask around
at the karaoke ba.

00:23:58.030 --> 00:23:59.310
Did you find out if there were police?

00:23:59.310 --> 00:23:59.920
I did check.

00:23:59.920 --> 00:24:01.480
I really couldn't find out.

00:24:01.680 --> 00:24:03.200
You went to see your girlfriend again,
didn't you?

00:24:03.200 --> 00:24:03.640
No.

00:24:04.200 --> 00:24:04.640
No.

00:24:04.960 --> 00:24:05.310
No.

00:24:05.310 --> 00:24:06.960
If not, who did you ask?

00:24:07.830 --> 00:24:08.640
Boss.

00:24:09.720 --> 00:24:10.720
Stop hitting me.

00:24:10.720 --> 00:24:11.510
Damn it!

00:24:13.480 --> 00:24:14.000
Ran.

00:24:14.240 --> 00:24:15.480
You're a seasoned married couple.

00:24:15.480 --> 00:24:17.030
Step back and you will see a broader view.

00:24:17.030 --> 00:24:18.340
What's the point?

00:24:18.480 --> 00:24:19.210
I've already

00:24:19.240 --> 00:24:20.240
lost everything.

00:24:20.750 --> 00:24:21.480
Ran,

00:24:21.790 --> 00:24:22.350
can you just

00:24:22.350 --> 00:24:23.920
do me this solid?

00:24:24.110 --> 00:24:25.060
Besides,

00:24:25.200 --> 00:24:26.200
you're a grown man.

00:24:26.200 --> 00:24:27.510
What's the real cost of an apology?

00:24:27.510 --> 00:24:28.710
It costs you nothing.

00:24:29.070 --> 00:24:30.590
I'm willing to do you this favor,

00:24:30.590 --> 00:24:31.440
but she won't.

00:24:31.830 --> 00:24:32.430
Now she

00:24:32.960 --> 00:24:34.290
doesn't care about you.

00:24:34.510 --> 00:24:35.750
She only cares about money.

00:24:35.750 --> 00:24:36.750
Anyway, our goal

00:24:36.920 --> 00:24:38.830
is to mend things, not to end things.

00:24:38.830 --> 00:24:39.640
You're a police officer,

00:24:39.640 --> 00:24:41.030
but you're the one
making a fuss about divorce.

00:24:41.030 --> 00:24:42.070
If the folks around here hear about it,

00:24:42.070 --> 00:24:43.110
it's not a good look.

00:24:43.110 --> 00:24:44.710
No, who said I want a divorce?

00:24:44.960 --> 00:24:45.590
She did?

00:24:45.790 --> 00:24:46.640
Well, if you're not getting a divorce,

00:24:46.640 --> 00:24:48.310
then why is she
staying at her parents' house?

00:24:48.310 --> 00:24:48.680
That's true.

00:24:48.680 --> 00:24:49.480
Furthermore,

00:24:49.550 --> 00:24:50.270
you two

00:24:50.270 --> 00:24:52.030
can't keep living separately like this,

00:24:52.030 --> 00:24:52.440
right?

00:24:52.720 --> 00:24:53.480
As an officer,

00:24:53.480 --> 00:24:54.920
you should make your marriage work

00:24:54.920 --> 00:24:56.920
and set an example for everyone, right?

00:24:56.920 --> 00:24:58.240
We're really fine.

00:24:58.480 --> 00:24:59.880
You two can rest assured.

00:25:00.880 --> 00:25:01.550
Ran.

00:25:02.110 --> 00:25:03.270
As for the murder case,

00:25:03.270 --> 00:25:04.640
have you caught the killer?

00:25:04.640 --> 00:25:05.890
Someone told me

00:25:06.000 --> 00:25:07.640
it was someone

00:25:07.640 --> 00:25:08.240
from the demolition company.

00:25:08.240 --> 00:25:09.040
Who said that?

00:25:09.400 --> 00:25:10.600
Tell me who said that.

00:25:10.920 --> 00:25:11.680
I'll bring him to the station

00:25:11.680 --> 00:25:12.590
for a proper questioning.

00:25:12.590 --> 00:25:13.030
Well,

00:25:13.030 --> 00:25:14.680
everyone's saying so.

00:25:14.680 --> 00:25:15.720
They said the demolition

00:25:15.720 --> 00:25:17.030
is managed by that Crazy Monk.

00:25:17.030 --> 00:25:17.960
I'm telling you,

00:25:18.030 --> 00:25:18.680
that guy

00:25:18.680 --> 00:25:20.140
is not a decent character.

00:25:20.200 --> 00:25:20.640
Yes.

00:25:21.270 --> 00:25:22.070
Alright then.

00:25:22.200 --> 00:25:23.310
Mrs. Qian, Mrs. Zhao,

00:25:23.310 --> 00:25:24.400
I understand

00:25:24.550 --> 00:25:25.680
what you're saying.

00:25:26.070 --> 00:25:27.790
I'll actively resolve my family matters.

00:25:27.790 --> 00:25:28.110
Okay.

00:25:28.110 --> 00:25:29.550
If you have any leads in the hutong,

00:25:29.550 --> 00:25:31.080
please let me know anytime.

00:25:31.440 --> 00:25:31.880
Sure.

00:25:32.030 --> 00:25:32.400
[Ping'anli Neighborhood Committee,
Nanhuaishu Subdistrict, Fengyang District]

00:25:32.400 --> 00:25:33.310
By the way, Ran.

00:25:33.480 --> 00:25:34.240
That,

00:25:34.440 --> 00:25:35.750
Beiping

00:25:35.750 --> 00:25:37.070
and her business partner...

00:25:37.070 --> 00:25:39.330
There's nothing wrong with them, right?

00:25:40.680 --> 00:25:41.880
What could be wrong?

00:25:41.970 --> 00:25:43.310
[Ping'anli Neighborhood Committee,
Nanhuaishu Subdistrict, Fengyang District]

00:25:43.310 --> 00:25:44.030
Good to hear.

00:25:44.030 --> 00:25:44.790
That's great.

00:25:44.790 --> 00:25:45.550
Safe riding.

00:25:51.310 --> 00:25:53.850
[Ping'anli Neighborhood Committee,
Nanhuaishu Subdistrict, Fengyang District]

00:25:58.030 --> 00:25:58.750
[Nanhuaishu Public Security
Joint Defense Team, Fengyang District]

00:25:58.750 --> 00:25:59.280
[Nanhuaishu Police Station,
Fengyang Branch, Yanchuan Police]

00:26:27.030 --> 00:26:27.590
Guys,

00:26:27.790 --> 00:26:29.390
line up the bicycles in a row.

00:26:30.880 --> 00:26:31.090
Make sure they're neat.

00:26:31.090 --> 00:26:35.090
[Love the People, Love Public Security,
Love Nanhuai]

00:26:36.700 --> 00:26:38.910
[Love the People, Love Public Security,
Love Nanhuai]

00:26:39.750 --> 00:26:40.750
Who are these for?

00:26:41.050 --> 00:26:41.250
[People's Public]

00:26:41.250 --> 00:26:41.790
For you,

00:26:41.790 --> 00:26:43.140
the Nanhuaishu Police Station.

00:26:43.140 --> 00:26:45.030
[Respectfully Presented to
Nanhuaishu Police Station, Ran Erchu]

00:26:45.030 --> 00:26:46.070
Ran Erchu?

00:26:46.920 --> 00:26:47.920
Who's Ran Erchu?

00:26:48.400 --> 00:26:49.460
You don't know him?

00:26:50.400 --> 00:26:52.330
We only have one person named Ran here.

00:26:52.330 --> 00:26:53.310
[Respectfully Presented to
Nanhuaishu Police Station, Ran Erchu]

00:26:53.310 --> 00:26:54.970
Who told you to deliver these?

00:26:55.270 --> 00:26:56.680
It's our Brother Monk.

00:26:57.440 --> 00:26:58.240
Brother Monk?

00:26:58.420 --> 00:27:00.030
Alright, guys, let's go.

00:27:00.070 --> 00:27:01.200
Your mentor is something.

00:27:01.200 --> 00:27:02.350
Even Crazy Monk is sending gifts.

00:27:02.350 --> 00:27:03.310
Such a grand gesture.

00:27:03.310 --> 00:27:06.550
[People's Public]

00:27:06.550 --> 00:27:07.510
Why did my mentor

00:27:07.510 --> 00:27:08.440
claim that he was

00:27:08.480 --> 00:27:09.540
from Division Two?

00:27:10.270 --> 00:27:12.130
You don't know about this, do you?

00:27:12.160 --> 00:27:13.160
Only Division Two of the City Bureau

00:27:13.160 --> 00:27:14.400
can handle these gangsters.

00:27:14.400 --> 00:27:15.480
Even if you say
you're from the Criminal Police Team,

00:27:15.480 --> 00:27:16.270
it won't help.

00:27:16.270 --> 00:27:16.960
Let alone

00:27:17.310 --> 00:27:19.090
this small Nanhuaishu Police Station.

00:27:19.090 --> 00:27:22.220
[People's Public]

00:27:22.510 --> 00:27:23.970
Crazy Monk is suspicious.

00:27:25.000 --> 00:27:26.330
He also has a black limo.

00:27:26.920 --> 00:27:27.790
Be sensible.

00:27:27.960 --> 00:27:29.960
He who pays the piper calls the tune.

00:27:30.400 --> 00:27:31.750
Will your mentor let you arrest him?

00:27:31.750 --> 00:27:32.350
Besides,

00:27:32.470 --> 00:27:33.240
do you think

00:27:33.440 --> 00:27:35.500
anyone can arrest this big gangster?

00:27:37.270 --> 00:27:38.530
It's better than mine.

00:27:39.400 --> 00:27:40.070
Hey, Ran.

00:27:40.270 --> 00:27:42.000
There are quite a few bicycles.

00:27:42.310 --> 00:27:44.370
Ran, you've got a good deal this time.

00:27:45.790 --> 00:27:46.440
Chief Zhu.

00:27:48.510 --> 00:27:49.310
Director Ran.

00:27:50.200 --> 00:27:51.730
This is really impressive.

00:27:51.830 --> 00:27:53.790
So should I take

00:27:53.790 --> 00:27:54.750
my bicycle or not?

00:27:54.750 --> 00:27:55.750
It's up to you.

00:27:56.030 --> 00:27:57.430
It's none of my business.

00:27:57.790 --> 00:27:59.650
I don't even know who Ran Erchu is.

00:27:59.920 --> 00:28:00.720
How come?

00:28:01.030 --> 00:28:03.630
A straight foot is not afraid of
a crooked shoe.

00:28:06.000 --> 00:28:07.720
Don't give me that nonsense.

00:28:09.000 --> 00:28:10.400
I just want to ask you one thing.

00:28:10.400 --> 00:28:11.270
Are you trying to extort money

00:28:11.270 --> 00:28:12.200
or what exactly?

00:28:12.550 --> 00:28:13.720
What extortion?

00:28:14.480 --> 00:28:14.880
Well,

00:28:16.230 --> 00:28:16.960
are you still

00:28:16.960 --> 00:28:18.420
investigating that case?

00:28:20.270 --> 00:28:21.220
Let me warn you.

00:28:21.440 --> 00:28:22.900
You're a veteran officer.

00:28:23.070 --> 00:28:24.000
I'm quite satisfied

00:28:24.000 --> 00:28:25.310
with your current state.

00:28:25.310 --> 00:28:26.790
But I still need to remind you

00:28:26.790 --> 00:28:28.000
that when you investigate cases
and locate people,

00:28:28.000 --> 00:28:29.600
you need to know your limits.

00:28:30.110 --> 00:28:31.880
For some people, you can question anytime.

00:28:31.880 --> 00:28:33.070
For others, you need solid evidence

00:28:33.070 --> 00:28:34.240
before you can go after them.

00:28:34.240 --> 00:28:35.310
Before questioning them, you need

00:28:35.310 --> 00:28:36.970
to file a report with me first.

00:28:46.110 --> 00:28:47.970
I'm saying this for your own good.

00:28:50.160 --> 00:28:52.070
If I know about these matters beforehand,

00:28:52.070 --> 00:28:53.600
I can cover for you, can't I?

00:28:54.880 --> 00:28:56.480
I'm just worried that maybe,

00:28:57.160 --> 00:28:58.110
what if we discover later

00:28:58.110 --> 00:28:59.570
that Crazy Wu didn't do it,

00:28:59.640 --> 00:29:01.680
what should we tell the leadership then?

00:29:01.680 --> 00:29:03.510
"Is this how you investigate cases?"

00:29:03.510 --> 00:29:03.960
No.

00:29:05.160 --> 00:29:06.750
Crazy Wu has already
jumped off the building.

00:29:06.750 --> 00:29:07.750
It's so obvious.

00:29:08.350 --> 00:29:09.880
The bottle was found at his place.

00:29:09.880 --> 00:29:11.480
He was known to be
mentally unstable in that precinct.

00:29:11.480 --> 00:29:12.830
Isn't this clearly suicide out of guilt?

00:29:12.830 --> 00:29:13.720
Even a lunatic would know

00:29:13.720 --> 00:29:14.720
about suicide from guilt.

00:29:14.720 --> 00:29:16.850
That line of thinking is quite normal.

00:29:17.000 --> 00:29:19.330
Besides, the knife hasn't been found yet.

00:29:21.900 --> 00:29:22.500
Fine then.

00:29:23.790 --> 00:29:24.650
Let me tell you,

00:29:24.750 --> 00:29:26.240
if you get any leads from Crazy Monk,

00:29:26.240 --> 00:29:27.350
report to the Criminal Police Team first.

00:29:27.350 --> 00:29:28.480
Don't keep it to yourself.

00:29:28.480 --> 00:29:29.240
Understood.

00:29:33.590 --> 00:29:34.920
I'll just say one thing.

00:29:35.240 --> 00:29:36.550
This hutong can be demolished,

00:29:36.550 --> 00:29:38.150
but we can't let morale drop.

00:29:50.590 --> 00:29:52.250
Five, six, extend right hand.

00:29:52.350 --> 00:29:53.010
Right hand.

00:29:53.400 --> 00:29:54.160
Left hand.

00:29:54.350 --> 00:29:56.030
Pat pat, return.

00:29:56.310 --> 00:29:57.960
Left arm, right arm.

00:29:58.240 --> 00:29:59.960
Pat pat, return.

00:30:00.270 --> 00:30:01.790
Right hand, left hand.

00:30:03.240 --> 00:30:04.110
One last time.

00:30:06.550 --> 00:30:07.350
Who is it?

00:30:11.920 --> 00:30:12.720
It's you, Xia.

00:30:15.240 --> 00:30:17.000
He forced me to come find you.

00:30:17.720 --> 00:30:18.350
Get lost.

00:30:36.270 --> 00:30:36.800
Brother.

00:30:37.480 --> 00:30:38.590
If you wanted to find me,

00:30:38.590 --> 00:30:39.960
you could have just paged me.

00:30:39.960 --> 00:30:41.360
Why come all the way here?

00:30:42.000 --> 00:30:43.200
Be careful, it's hot.

00:30:43.960 --> 00:30:45.110
Weren't you avoiding me?

00:30:45.110 --> 00:30:45.880
No, I wasn't.

00:30:45.880 --> 00:30:47.010
I couldn't find you.

00:30:48.920 --> 00:30:49.980
My pager is broken.

00:30:51.640 --> 00:30:52.960
How did you get hurt?

00:30:53.000 --> 00:30:53.790
Let me see.

00:30:54.550 --> 00:30:55.550
Let me take a look.

00:30:55.960 --> 00:30:56.680
Wait, wait.

00:30:56.750 --> 00:30:57.480
Let me ask you

00:30:57.550 --> 00:30:58.210
something.

00:30:58.830 --> 00:31:00.830
You clearly knew
there were police that day.

00:31:00.830 --> 00:31:02.560
Why didn't you tell me earlier?

00:31:04.030 --> 00:31:05.400
If I told you the police were there,

00:31:05.400 --> 00:31:06.920
you wouldn't have come.

00:31:08.270 --> 00:31:09.400
Besides, I didn't know

00:31:09.400 --> 00:31:11.460
you were going there to make trouble.

00:31:12.350 --> 00:31:13.880
What's it to you?

00:31:15.510 --> 00:31:17.400
The more I think about it,
the angrier I get.

00:31:17.400 --> 00:31:18.350
What do you mean?

00:31:18.640 --> 00:31:20.200
You set me up on purpose, didn't you?

00:31:20.200 --> 00:31:22.200
I'm going to beat you to death today!

00:33:16.300 --> 00:33:18.480
[ADAN&EVE]

00:33:18.480 --> 00:33:19.080
Actually,

00:33:19.110 --> 00:33:20.240
when you buy instant noodles later,

00:33:20.240 --> 00:33:21.350
you'd better get

00:33:21.400 --> 00:33:22.110
Master Kang's.

00:33:22.110 --> 00:33:23.830
Master Kang's tastes better
than Huafeng's.

00:33:23.830 --> 00:33:25.640
[Come in for a treat]

00:33:25.640 --> 00:33:27.770
Aren't they all just instant noodles?

00:33:28.030 --> 00:33:29.560
Better to save where we can.

00:33:30.830 --> 00:33:31.350
Ping.

00:33:32.750 --> 00:33:33.950
Let's be honest here.

00:33:34.110 --> 00:33:34.960
If by the end of the month,

00:33:34.960 --> 00:33:36.680
this shop still isn't making money,

00:33:36.680 --> 00:33:38.140
we'd better close it down.

00:33:38.750 --> 00:33:39.590
All the losses

00:33:39.830 --> 00:33:40.560
will be on me.

00:33:44.830 --> 00:33:46.830
Let's hang in there a little longer.

00:33:51.350 --> 00:33:53.030
Chinese Adam and Eve.

00:33:53.410 --> 00:33:53.880
[ADAN&EVE]

00:33:53.880 --> 00:33:55.080
This is really great.

00:33:55.920 --> 00:33:56.550
Hello.

00:34:10.400 --> 00:34:11.000
All right.

00:34:36.550 --> 00:34:37.280
It's Ran.

00:34:53.070 --> 00:34:59.500
[Map of Streets and Alleys
in Fengyang District]

00:35:00.150 --> 00:35:01.320
He's really something.

00:35:01.320 --> 00:35:02.030
Really?

00:35:02.070 --> 00:35:02.510
It's true.

00:35:02.510 --> 00:35:03.550
Ran is indeed...

00:35:03.630 --> 00:35:04.280
You have to admit.

00:35:04.280 --> 00:35:05.680
He's got that something,

00:35:06.320 --> 00:35:06.880
right?

00:35:07.910 --> 00:35:08.710
[Model Organization]

00:35:08.710 --> 00:35:09.920
You're having a meal here.

00:35:09.920 --> 00:35:10.630
What's up?

00:35:20.000 --> 00:35:20.860
What is it, Xue?

00:35:21.510 --> 00:35:23.280
If you make it big someday,

00:35:23.510 --> 00:35:24.770
don't forget about me.

00:35:25.230 --> 00:35:26.230
What do you mean?

00:35:26.440 --> 00:35:28.040
Learn well from your mentor,

00:35:28.320 --> 00:35:30.030
and you'll definitely succeed.

00:35:30.030 --> 00:35:30.710
Look, Xue,

00:35:30.710 --> 00:35:32.150
just be straight with me.

00:35:32.590 --> 00:35:34.320
Let's not play detective here.

00:35:34.590 --> 00:35:35.480
I just found out

00:35:35.760 --> 00:35:36.760
the company handling demolition

00:35:36.760 --> 00:35:38.560
in our precinct is Crazy Monk's.

00:35:38.960 --> 00:35:40.690
Ran immediately made his move.

00:35:41.800 --> 00:35:42.150
But wait,

00:35:42.150 --> 00:35:43.680
we only met Crazy Monk once,

00:35:43.800 --> 00:35:45.460
and we almost got into a fight.

00:35:49.070 --> 00:35:50.510
The Bodhisattva lowers his brow,

00:35:50.510 --> 00:35:51.960
the Vajra glares in wrath.

00:35:51.960 --> 00:35:53.360
These are all tactics.

00:35:54.150 --> 00:35:55.440
Your mentor, Ran...

00:36:07.930 --> 00:36:12.790
[People's Public]

00:36:20.630 --> 00:36:21.070
Hello,

00:36:21.230 --> 00:36:22.960
I'm from Nanhuaishu Police Station.

00:36:22.960 --> 00:36:23.960
My badge number is

00:36:24.000 --> 00:36:25.230
5816328.

00:36:25.930 --> 00:36:27.070
May I ask

00:36:27.630 --> 00:36:29.630
if Crazy Monk is from your precinct?

00:36:30.760 --> 00:36:31.690
What's his name?

00:36:33.960 --> 00:36:34.840
Zhu Dachuan.

00:36:38.280 --> 00:36:39.550
On May 18th,

00:36:39.840 --> 00:36:41.570
did Crazy Monk wreck your shop?

00:36:41.760 --> 00:36:42.630
Officer,

00:36:42.960 --> 00:36:43.920
Monk

00:36:44.190 --> 00:36:45.720
is now my business partner.

00:36:45.960 --> 00:36:46.560
Look here.

00:36:46.920 --> 00:36:48.450
He invested in all of these.

00:36:51.070 --> 00:36:51.760
He smashed it first

00:36:51.760 --> 00:36:53.550
and then hires construction crews
to repair.

00:36:53.550 --> 00:36:55.210
That's considered buying in?

00:36:56.400 --> 00:36:57.960
What did you do to piss him off?

00:36:57.960 --> 00:36:59.490
How would I dare offend him?

00:36:59.670 --> 00:37:02.030
Live life to the fullest!

00:37:04.590 --> 00:37:05.630
Monk.

00:37:19.590 --> 00:37:20.390
Feeling good?

00:37:22.360 --> 00:37:23.360
Comfortable?

00:37:27.480 --> 00:37:29.510
Did I let you touch me?

00:37:31.320 --> 00:37:32.450
What's wrong, Monk?

00:37:32.510 --> 00:37:33.760
Monk, what are you doing?

00:37:33.760 --> 00:37:35.190
What are you doing, Monk?

00:37:35.960 --> 00:37:37.630
Monk, stop smashing things!

00:37:38.230 --> 00:37:39.360
What's wrong, Monk?

00:37:39.840 --> 00:37:41.360
Stop smashing, Monk!

00:37:41.400 --> 00:37:43.030
Monk, please stop!

00:37:43.320 --> 00:37:45.760
Stop smashing. Just tell me what's wrong.

00:37:46.030 --> 00:37:47.760
Please, Monk, I'm begging you.

00:37:47.920 --> 00:37:48.710
Monk.

00:37:48.710 --> 00:37:55.640
[Video Room]

00:37:57.670 --> 00:37:58.630
Is Xia here?

00:37:59.280 --> 00:38:00.280
What is it, officer?

00:38:00.280 --> 00:38:01.540
Don't you remember me?

00:38:01.670 --> 00:38:03.070
I came here before with my mentor,

00:38:03.070 --> 00:38:04.190
looking for a dog.

00:38:05.400 --> 00:38:06.710
You're Ran's apprentice!

00:38:06.710 --> 00:38:07.880
Xia is my cousin.

00:38:08.190 --> 00:38:08.670
No. What's going on?

00:38:08.670 --> 00:38:09.930
I'm good. Where is she?

00:38:10.360 --> 00:38:10.880
She-

00:38:10.960 --> 00:38:11.800
just-

00:38:12.400 --> 00:38:13.030
went out.

00:38:15.000 --> 00:38:15.670
Brother,

00:38:15.960 --> 00:38:17.090
I'm heading to work.

00:38:17.960 --> 00:38:19.110
You're Xia, right?

00:38:25.550 --> 00:38:25.680
Can you remember anything else?

00:38:25.680 --> 00:38:26.670
[Double Feature]

00:38:26.670 --> 00:38:27.320
Go on.

00:38:30.920 --> 00:38:31.510
[Weekend Special]

00:38:31.510 --> 00:38:32.800
That's all about it.

00:38:33.150 --> 00:38:34.670
This doesn't concern you. Now get inside.

00:38:34.670 --> 00:38:35.200
Alright.

00:38:38.000 --> 00:38:39.400
That matches what I know.

00:38:39.670 --> 00:38:40.630
Do you know why

00:38:40.670 --> 00:38:42.000
he suddenly went crazy?

00:38:42.030 --> 00:38:43.110
How would I know?

00:38:44.110 --> 00:38:45.360
It's a problem
if you ignore him completely,

00:38:45.360 --> 00:38:46.800
but it's also a problem
if you engage with him too much.

00:38:46.800 --> 00:38:48.510
Damned if I do, damned if I don't.

00:38:48.510 --> 00:38:50.040
His henchman is also crazy.

00:38:50.400 --> 00:38:51.480
A few days ago, that Fat Cat

00:38:51.480 --> 00:38:52.940
nearly beat Lili to death.

00:38:53.110 --> 00:38:53.710
Lili?

00:38:54.760 --> 00:38:56.400
Is she from the Little Erhei's

00:38:56.400 --> 00:38:57.070
Karaoke Bar?

00:38:57.070 --> 00:38:59.000
Yes, we're from the same hometown.

00:39:04.510 --> 00:39:05.710
It should be this way.

00:39:15.630 --> 00:39:16.150
Come on.

00:39:26.070 --> 00:39:26.670
Excuse me,

00:39:26.800 --> 00:39:27.280
Sir.

00:39:27.960 --> 00:39:29.510
Where did Crazy Monk's family

00:39:29.510 --> 00:39:30.510
move to?

00:39:32.960 --> 00:39:33.690
Zhu Dachuan.

00:39:34.190 --> 00:39:34.880
The Zhu's.

00:39:35.550 --> 00:39:36.590
Where did his family move to?

00:39:36.590 --> 00:39:37.520
How would I know?

00:39:52.670 --> 00:39:56.670
Waves burst, waves roll,

00:39:57.480 --> 00:40:01.920
ten thousand miles
of torrents never cease.

00:40:02.510 --> 00:40:04.480
They wash clean

00:40:04.880 --> 00:40:07.110
the slate of all human endeavors.

00:40:07.550 --> 00:40:08.410
All are lost...

00:40:13.590 --> 00:40:15.110
Don't you remember me?

00:40:16.360 --> 00:40:17.510
We've met before.

00:40:18.070 --> 00:40:19.150
I'm from Nanhuaishu

00:40:19.150 --> 00:40:20.080
Police Station.

00:40:21.030 --> 00:40:22.320
I remember you, Zhao.

00:40:23.590 --> 00:40:25.250
Is this an inconvenient time?

00:40:25.510 --> 00:40:26.320
No, it's fine.

00:40:26.440 --> 00:40:27.370
Come in, please.

00:40:31.000 --> 00:40:32.660
I'm not wearing makeup today,

00:40:33.150 --> 00:40:34.410
so I don't look my best.

00:40:35.960 --> 00:40:37.400
I heard you were injured.

00:40:38.190 --> 00:40:39.590
I brought you something.

00:40:41.190 --> 00:40:42.070
Are you okay?

00:40:43.480 --> 00:40:44.010
I'm fine.

00:40:44.480 --> 00:40:45.000
I was

00:40:45.360 --> 00:40:47.290
walking at night and accidentally

00:40:47.590 --> 00:40:48.920
fell into a well.

00:40:49.760 --> 00:40:50.550
Is it serious?

00:40:50.550 --> 00:40:51.280
Not serious.

00:40:52.360 --> 00:40:53.110
Just a bump.

00:40:54.480 --> 00:40:55.550
Some mischievous kid

00:40:55.550 --> 00:40:56.950
stole the manhole cover.

00:40:59.000 --> 00:41:01.000
It's Fat Cat who did it to you, right?

00:41:07.480 --> 00:41:08.540
Why did he beat you?

00:41:09.550 --> 00:41:10.410
Because of you.

00:41:10.760 --> 00:41:11.560
Because of me?

00:41:13.400 --> 00:41:15.320
That day when he came to make trouble.

00:41:15.320 --> 00:41:16.030
I was at the door.

00:41:16.030 --> 00:41:17.490
He asked me who was inside.

00:41:18.070 --> 00:41:18.630
I didn't tell him

00:41:18.630 --> 00:41:20.230
that you police were inside.

00:41:20.670 --> 00:41:21.630
Then his boss

00:41:21.630 --> 00:41:22.230
blamed him for it.

00:41:22.230 --> 00:41:23.290
So he was beaten up.

00:41:23.920 --> 00:41:25.720
Their boss is Crazy Monk, right?

00:41:28.230 --> 00:41:29.000
Where do he and Crazy Monk

00:41:29.000 --> 00:41:30.000
usually hang out?

00:41:32.190 --> 00:41:33.000
I don't know.

00:41:34.510 --> 00:41:35.190
Has he ever told you

00:41:35.190 --> 00:41:36.720
anything about Crazy Monk?

00:41:44.360 --> 00:41:44.920
Brother.

00:41:45.510 --> 00:41:47.000
So you didn't come to visit me.

00:41:47.000 --> 00:41:48.530
You came to interrogate me.

00:41:55.150 --> 00:41:56.950
I'm still happy about it though.

00:41:58.480 --> 00:41:59.400
To be honest.

00:42:00.190 --> 00:42:01.150
Actually, many customers

00:42:01.150 --> 00:42:02.190
like to persuade me to quit this life

00:42:02.190 --> 00:42:03.590
after they get drunk,

00:42:04.480 --> 00:42:05.840
especially those intellectuals.

00:42:05.840 --> 00:42:07.570
They enjoy doing this the most.

00:42:07.630 --> 00:42:09.360
At first, I was really touched,

00:42:10.150 --> 00:42:11.880
and thought they were looking out for me.

00:42:11.880 --> 00:42:13.280
Later I realized

00:42:13.630 --> 00:42:16.190
they just wanted free services.

00:42:16.960 --> 00:42:17.840
When I saw you that time

00:42:17.840 --> 00:42:19.440
I thought you were like them.

00:42:22.400 --> 00:42:23.930
But you came to see me today,

00:42:24.070 --> 00:42:25.530
and even brought me gifts.

00:42:26.710 --> 00:42:27.360
I know

00:42:27.360 --> 00:42:28.960
you're different from them.

00:42:33.280 --> 00:42:34.410
I'm really touched.

00:42:34.840 --> 00:42:35.300
Really.

00:42:36.630 --> 00:42:37.630
From the bottom of my heart,

00:42:37.630 --> 00:42:39.090
I consider you my brother.

00:42:39.800 --> 00:42:41.730
You'd better call me Officer Zhao.

00:42:46.630 --> 00:42:47.190
But I do

00:42:47.190 --> 00:42:49.520
sincerely hope you turn your life around.

00:42:50.280 --> 00:42:51.410
Okay, Officer Zhao.

00:42:51.920 --> 00:42:52.760
Then tell me.

00:42:53.710 --> 00:42:55.150
I'm not well educated,

00:42:55.320 --> 00:42:57.320
and have no good family background.

00:42:57.440 --> 00:42:59.000
I'm not exactly a tough cookie, you know?

00:42:59.000 --> 00:43:00.330
I still want a good life.

00:43:00.880 --> 00:43:02.190
What could I do

00:43:02.190 --> 00:43:03.720
if I changed my profession?

00:43:05.710 --> 00:43:07.170
Even if I wanted to change,

00:43:07.710 --> 00:43:09.800
would those people let me go?

00:43:12.190 --> 00:43:14.250
I can help you deal with those people.

00:43:15.440 --> 00:43:17.170
Your life is your own decision.

00:43:18.920 --> 00:43:19.720
Officer Zhao.

00:43:21.670 --> 00:43:22.670
Fat Cat and his gang usually

00:43:22.670 --> 00:43:23.920
stay at the auto repair shop

00:43:23.920 --> 00:43:25.050
in the east suburbs.

00:43:26.230 --> 00:43:26.840
Thank you.

00:44:01.110 --> 00:44:02.960
Little Erhei's car is 5.7 meters.

00:44:02.960 --> 00:44:03.360
What about me?

00:44:03.360 --> 00:44:04.710
Mine should be at least 5.9 meters.

00:44:04.710 --> 00:44:05.760
Even if we stretch it,

00:44:05.760 --> 00:44:06.820
it won't be sturdy.

00:44:06.920 --> 00:44:08.110
I don't care.

00:44:08.630 --> 00:44:10.490
Even if it's just by a centimeter,

00:44:10.510 --> 00:44:12.170
mine has to be longer than his.

00:44:14.320 --> 00:44:15.960
Stop talking nonsense!

00:44:16.880 --> 00:44:18.590
Just do whatever he told you to.

00:44:18.590 --> 00:44:19.990
Take it apart and redo it.

00:44:48.000 --> 00:44:48.840
Who is Fat Cat?

00:44:53.190 --> 00:44:54.550
What an idiot.

00:44:56.630 --> 00:44:57.830
I don't care who it is.

00:44:58.760 --> 00:45:00.290
Tell me where Crazy Monk is.

00:45:09.440 --> 00:45:10.360
You are...

00:45:11.230 --> 00:45:13.490
A police officer from the local station.

00:45:14.030 --> 00:45:14.920
Officer,

00:45:15.110 --> 00:45:16.840
what business do you have with him?

00:45:16.840 --> 00:45:18.440
Take him in for questioning.

00:45:23.960 --> 00:45:25.890
I was just teasing you a little bit.

00:45:26.150 --> 00:45:27.630
I recognize you now.

00:45:29.440 --> 00:45:31.360
Aren't you one of Little Erhei's men?

00:45:31.360 --> 00:45:32.230
Remember him?

00:45:32.430 --> 00:45:33.630
That day at the nightclub,

00:45:33.630 --> 00:45:35.000
this bastard can really fight.

00:45:35.000 --> 00:45:35.630
That's him.

00:45:35.630 --> 00:45:36.840
And now you're here playing cop?

00:45:36.840 --> 00:45:38.230
You're the one who beat me up last time.

00:45:38.230 --> 00:45:38.960
Don't get physical.

00:45:38.960 --> 00:45:40.480
Call me James Bond!

00:45:41.550 --> 00:45:42.400
So what if I do?

00:45:42.440 --> 00:45:43.040
What's up?

00:45:43.710 --> 00:45:45.440
What's wrong with pushing you?

00:45:47.030 --> 00:45:47.820
Let go of him!

00:45:48.070 --> 00:45:49.270
What's going on here?

00:46:14.630 --> 00:46:15.280
Alright.

00:46:29.110 --> 00:46:30.840
My mom didn't allow me to drink.

00:46:32.000 --> 00:46:32.550
I told her

00:46:32.590 --> 00:46:34.520
not to bother me when I'm drinking,

00:46:34.710 --> 00:46:36.840
but she insisted on grabbing my glass.

00:46:37.150 --> 00:46:38.190
I gave her a heavy over-shoulder throw

00:46:38.190 --> 00:46:39.790
and tossed her to the ground.

00:46:41.110 --> 00:46:41.920
Since then,

00:46:42.630 --> 00:46:45.230
she never again
tried to stop me from drinking.

00:46:45.230 --> 00:46:46.430
Interesting, right?

00:46:47.150 --> 00:46:48.000
Not at all.

00:46:51.510 --> 00:46:52.550
I...

00:46:53.230 --> 00:46:54.590
I used to sell fruit.

00:46:56.030 --> 00:46:57.430
There was a crippled man.

00:46:57.630 --> 00:47:00.190
He showed me his disability card
and begged for some every day.

00:47:00.190 --> 00:47:01.450
I always gave him some.

00:47:03.230 --> 00:47:04.290
He called me a fool.

00:47:05.800 --> 00:47:07.000
I had no choice.

00:47:07.630 --> 00:47:08.760
I felt sorry for him.

00:47:09.590 --> 00:47:11.630
Then one day, I really got fed up.

00:47:12.480 --> 00:47:14.410
I snatched up a knife in an instant.

00:47:15.190 --> 00:47:16.320
He said, "Come on, don't do this, bro!

00:47:16.320 --> 00:47:17.380
Was it necessary?"

00:47:17.760 --> 00:47:20.070
I just laid into him.

00:47:21.000 --> 00:47:21.760
Since then,

00:47:21.760 --> 00:47:23.490
he called me brother every day.

00:47:24.110 --> 00:47:25.440
Interesting, isn't it?

00:47:26.190 --> 00:47:27.000
Not at all.

00:47:29.110 --> 00:47:29.710
Either

00:47:31.920 --> 00:47:34.070
you beat them into submission today,

00:47:35.840 --> 00:47:36.400
or

00:47:37.440 --> 00:47:38.970
you're not going anywhere.

00:47:40.960 --> 00:47:43.160
If you've got the guts, beat me to death.

00:47:44.400 --> 00:47:45.760
See who dares to throw the final punch

00:47:45.760 --> 00:47:47.620
âthat one gets the death penalty.

00:47:48.670 --> 00:47:49.550
You know,

00:47:50.920 --> 00:47:52.520
those who truly earn respect

00:47:55.110 --> 00:47:56.570
are already underground,

00:47:58.710 --> 00:47:59.920
just like my mother.

00:48:01.000 --> 00:48:02.330
Interesting, isn't it?

00:48:03.630 --> 00:48:04.960
Not at all.

00:48:11.510 --> 00:48:12.910
But you're interesting.

00:48:15.030 --> 00:48:16.000
My Cadillac

00:48:16.000 --> 00:48:17.260
needs to be stretched.

00:48:17.840 --> 00:48:19.360
It needs to be longer.